   <script type="text/javascript">
    &lt;!--
function fnTrapKD(btnID, event){
btn = findObj(btnID);
 if (document.all){
  if (event.keyCode == 13){
   event.returnValue=false;
   event.cancel = true;
   invokeClick(btn);
   btn.disabled = true;
  }
 }
 else if (document.getElementById){
  if (event.which == 13){
   event.returnValue=false;
   event.cancel = true;
   btn.focus();
   invokeClick(btn);
   btn.disabled = true;
  }
 }
 else if(document.layers){
  if(event.which == 13){
   event.returnValue=false;
   event.cancel = true;
   btn.focus();
   invokeClick(btn);
   btn.disabled = true;
  }
 }
}

// Handles hyperlink element click() bug on Safari
function invokeClick(elem)
{
  if (elem &amp;&amp; elem.tagName == 'A')
    eval(elem.href);
  else
    elem.click();
}

function findObj(n, d) { 
	var p,i,x;  
	if(!d) 
		d=document; 
	if((p=n.indexOf("?"))&gt;0 &amp;&amp; parent.frames.length) {
		d=parent.frames[n.substring(p+1)].document; 
		n=n.substring(0,p);
	}
	if(!(x=d[n])&amp;&amp;d.all) 
		x=d.all[n]; 
	for (i=0;!x&amp;&amp;i&lt;d.forms.length;i++) 
		x=d.forms[i][n];
	for(i=0;!x&amp;&amp;d.layers&amp;&amp;i&lt;d.layers.length;i++) 
		x=findObj(n,d.layers[i].document);
	if(!x &amp;&amp; d.getElementById) 
		x=d.getElementById(n); 
	return x;
}
// --&gt;
